item.title: Music Love God
item.description: It’s quite unnerving sometime on what you stumble upon in Life & on the internet. In today’s world of music where lyrics mean nothing some just keep it alive. This is a post on what I just stumbled upon - this beautiful song, if you ever struggled or ever been through your downside of life or you are now feeling low, this a beautiful song that can touch your soul. Yep, music touches your soul like love does.
